      "message": "[warning] Line 90: Visibility behavior change: `showPresenceIndicator: Presence !\u003d\u003d undefined` is true even when `Presence \u003d\u003d\u003d 0` (offline), whereas the previous `Presence !\u003d\u003d undefined ? Presence : false` evaluated to a falsy 0 and hid the indicator for offline contacts. Combined with the new PresenceIndicator styling (Offline -\u003e transparent fill + `textColorHoveredHighContrast` border), offline contacts will now render a hollow ring where nothing was shown before. The same change applies to ConversationPickerItemDelegate.qml:48 and ContactPickerItemDelegate.qml:53. If displaying an offline ring is intended, please note it in the commit message; otherwise restore the prior \u0027hidden when offline\u0027 behavior, e.g. `showPresenceIndicator: Presence !\u003d\u003d undefined \u0026\u0026 Presence \u003e 0`.",
